</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_428" id="213v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Boslaw, herren czu Swannemberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Hirsfogel, <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan></add>, und fraw Agnes, die Ulman
                        Stromerin, unser burgerin, wie daz Johan Hannowicz,
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> diener, den Markart, des
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Hirsfogels, und den
                                <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, der
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Stromeyrin schreyber, gefangen und auf
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> slosz <add>czu</add>
<expan>Swanne<ex>m</ex>b<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<add>gefürt</add>
<expan>hab</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> diener daran weysen <add>wollet</add>, daz er
                        die <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burger und burgerin schreyber ledig lasse.
                        Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
